  <section class="row-fluid">
    <div class="span6 columns">
      <p>Beyond these questions, the significance of the Geneva Bible can not be overstated.</p>

      <p>The Geneva Bible is the most revolutionary of all English Bibles, it was the first English version to be translated entirely from the original languages, it was read by William Shakespeare when he wasn't writing a tragedy, and it was brought to America by the Puritans riding on the Mayflower thus greatly influencing the colonial culture of early American life. <sup id="fnref:1.4" class="footnote"><a href="/about#fn:1.4">4</a>,</sup> <sup id="fnref:1.5" class="footnote"><a href="/about#fn:1.5">5</a></sup></p>
    </div>

    <div class="span6 columns">
      <p>The rest of this site reflects my interest in all things &#0147;Jack&#0148;&#045; a labour of love, maybe an obsession, or simple boredom, I don&#039;t really know.</p>
      
